    "description": "快进入《发条人惊魂夜》的奇妙世界吧！在这座闹鬼的城堡里，你和你的好友将化身发条人相互猜忌。在这里你将体验到——<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >※昼夜交替</h2>白天是发条人的主场，夜晚则是内鬼的舞台。在昼夜交替之间审时度势，为你的阵营赢得优势。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213340/extras/e9ba0e636c6451200dfabcef6c5aaea5.poster.avif?t=1673938848\" width=700 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213340/extras/e9ba0e636c6451200dfabcef6c5aaea5.webm?t=1673938848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213340/extras/e9ba0e636c6451200dfabcef6c5aaea5.mp4?t=1673938848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >※合作撤离</h2>齐心协力完成任务，寻找撤离点，争分夺秒地逃出城堡，享受共赢带来的成就感。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213340/extras/13302ac177268fcc291eda930a1448c8.poster.avif?t=1673938848\" width=702 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213340/extras/13302ac177268fcc291eda930a1448c8.webm?t=1673938848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213340/extras/13302ac177268fcc291eda930a1448c8.mp4?t=1673938848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >※猎杀与逃亡</h2>夜幕降临时，内鬼变为强大的夜魔猎杀发条人，发条人用尽一切手段保命，双方将上演一场紧张刺激的追逐好戏。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213340/extras/0ead075ee1c264536a42f6fbc6a8cf88.poster.avif?t=1673938848\" width=702 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213340/extras/0ead075ee1c264536a42f6fbc6a8cf88.webm?t=1673938848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213340/extras/0ead075ee1c264536a42f6fbc6a8cf88.mp4?t=1673938848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >※唇枪舌战</h2>白天发条人拥有公投的权利，召开电话会议指控某人，激烈辩驳，说服大家放逐你的“敌人”。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213340/extras/df3f103454b79ec486288d0321acb9d3.poster.avif?t=1673938848\" width=702 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213340/extras/df3f103454b79ec486288d0321acb9d3.webm?t=1673938848\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2213340/extras/df3f103454b79ec486288d0321acb9d3.mp4?t=1673938848\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
